{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.080", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.680", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.160", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.800", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Am 4.\u00a0Oktober 1957 ereilte die USA etwas, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.080", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was in die Geschichte als Sputnik-Schock eingegangen ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.560", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was war geschehen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.640", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der damaligen Sowjetunion war es gelungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.280", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein unbemanntes Raumschiff, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.000", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Sputnik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.320", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ins All zu schicken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.560", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Niemand in den USA hatte das der Sowjetunion zugetraut. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.400", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Schlussfolgerungen in den USA waren allerdings bemerkenswert und sind f\u00fcr uns noch heute lehrreich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.280", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es wurde n\u00e4mlich ein breites Stipendienprogramm aufgelegt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.400", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar ausdr\u00fccklich f\u00fcr Kinder aus Nichtakademikerfamilien. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.480", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man hatte erkannt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.840", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es nicht reicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.720", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sich die Eliten nur aus sich selbst rekrutieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.520", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.320", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Idee m\u00fcssen wir aufgreifen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.400", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.040", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bildungsmauer zwischen oben und unten in unserem Land ist hoch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.560", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unverantwortlich hoch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.680", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von 100\u00a0Kindern aus Akademikerfamilien beginnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.040", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "statistisch gesehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.280", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "79 ein Hochschulstudium. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.440", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei Nichtakademikern schaffen gerade einmal 27 von 100\u00a0Kindern den Sprung an die Hochschule. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.800", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind die Ergebnisse einer aktuellen Untersuchung des Deutschen Zentrums f\u00fcr Hochschul- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.440", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Wissenschaftsforschung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.200", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "An der Ungleichverteilung der Aufstiegschancen hat sich in den letzten elf Jahren kaum etwas ver\u00e4ndert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.080", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Ministerin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.360", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist Ihre Aufgabe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.400", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Bildungsmauern endlich niederzurei\u00dfen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.400", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr Eltern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.480", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wenig Geld haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.520", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bedeutet ein Studium der Kinder ein gro\u00dfes Risiko. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.600", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das darf nicht sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.400", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darum fordert Die Linke ein elternunabh\u00e4ngiges BAf\u00f6G. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.000", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen das finanzieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.000", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir uns von der roten Null verabschieden und Reichtum endlich gerecht besteuern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.200", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der Wissenschaft selbst und in der Gesellschaft insgesamt wird \u00fcber eine Glaubw\u00fcrdigkeitskrise der Wissenschaft diskutiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.600", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.000", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir m\u00fcssen Wissenschaft neu denken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.680", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Ministerin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.000", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben in mehreren \u00f6ffentlichen Veranstaltungen die Wissenschaft aufgefordert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.760", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "st\u00e4rker zu kommunizieren und zu erkl\u00e4ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.600", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Doch ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.640", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir haben nicht nur ein Kommunikationsproblem. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.600", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte mit Erlaubnis des Pr\u00e4sidenten an dieser Stelle den Klimaforscher Hans Joachim Schellnhuber zitieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.400", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er schreibt in der Auseinandersetzung mit Donald Trump und den Leugnern des Klimawandels"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.880", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.360", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da melden sich die Richtigen zu Wort\u00a0\u2013:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.920", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2026\u00a0die Gr\u00fcndungsv\u00e4ter der Aufkl\u00e4rung erkl\u00e4rten\u00a0\u2026 mit Nachdruck, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.080", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Erkenntnis ohne Ethik wertlos ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.920", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Ethik stellt an Forscher zwei Anspr\u00fcche. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.320", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4mlich sich bei der Suche nach der Wahrheit nicht von Interessen beeinflussen zu lassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.480", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und die aufgefundenen Wahrheiten nach Ma\u00dfgabe der humanistischen Werte in den Dienst der Gesellschaft zu stellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.520", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das bedeutet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.160", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mitverantwortung f\u00fcr die Nutzung\u00a0\u2026 der eigenen Erkenntnisse zu \u00fcbernehmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.680", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dem kann ich nur voll zustimmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.840", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Augenblick muss sich die Wissenschaft gegen Falsch\u00admeldungen wehren; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.640", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie muss sich aber auch gegen einen gro\u00dfen Verwertungsdruck wehren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.160", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen hier als Politikerinnen und Politiker an ihrer Seite stehen und die Wissenschaft davor sch\u00fctzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.480", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von Konzernen immer mehr in ihren Dienst gezwungen zu werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.200", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was f\u00fcr VW oder BASF gut ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.400", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss automatisch auch f\u00fcr die Gesellschaft gut sein! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.640", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wissen doch alle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.640", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.920", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dem nicht so ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.720", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen keine Appelle der Bundesregierung an die Wissenschaft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.120", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen verl\u00e4ssliche Rahmenbedingungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.560", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viele Wissenschaftlerinnen und Wissenschaftler hangeln sich von einer befristeten Stelle zur n\u00e4chsten; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.400", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das darf so nicht weitergehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.400", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind gezwungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.560", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wertvolle Zeit mit endlosen Projektantr\u00e4gen und f\u00fcr die Einwerbung von Drittmitteln zu verschwenden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.000", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Grundgesetz steht:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.680", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kunst und Wissenschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.720", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Forschung und Lehre sind frei."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.280", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.800", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das muss ich hinzuf\u00fcgen\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.080", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht frei von den Gesetzen des Kapitalismus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.120", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mein Appell: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.800", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verteidigen wir das Grundgesetz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.440", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar in seinem Wortlaut!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.760", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.040", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.040", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Dr.\u00a0L\u00f6tzsch.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.000", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als N\u00e4chstes f\u00fcr die Fraktion B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen der Kollege Kai Gehring."
   ]
  }
 ]
